                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2605.01234/2605.01234v1/imgs/teaser_figure.png",
                "caption": "Figure 1.“Lift-First Pipeline” to generate TT4D, a massive multimodal 140+ hour dataset that recovers camera parameters, 3D ball positions, ball spin, and 3D human meshesover timefrom general-view broadcast videos.\nInverting traditional logic, we directly lift entire sequences from 2D ball tracks to 3D trajectories, bypassing fragile 2D-based time segmentation.",
                "position": 312
            }
        ]
